{"tid":972658,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"其實絲打們如果有得選擇會唔會做全職家庭主婦？","createTime":"2019-01-07T13:54:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-08T01:34:38.000Z","uid":154054,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76600bdc5b0193ac949b151b6d2123ffda6fd8f7","tid":972658,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:54:41.000Z","msg":"好既係唔洗受返工既氣，辦公室政治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日hea下就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 舒舒服服<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n壞既係自己冇收入，萬一同個老公感情唔好問佢攞買餸錢都好似乞咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且日日係屋企圈子可能會越黎越細<br />\n<br />\n女人有自己收入可以保障自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbac23257e9d071fc0e2b6352930a2410ce31612","tid":972658,"uid":31173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:55:37.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"42a8286efcc4f228aab9815870d3a426d2c6a406","tid":972658,"uid":40766,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 返半職最爽"},{"pid":"e043d1e6be95ceb36839b1ff4dad3365ef24cbfc","tid":972658,"uid":867,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:57:37.000Z","msg":"返工啦梗係<br />\n唔想比條佬鏈撚住春袋 幾時都要保障下自己<br />\n加上你做緊全職主婦 你成個世界同埋知識同埋見識都會停落嚟<br />\n然後你見到嘅同相處落嘅都係一啲冇腦嘅師奶<br />\n個人會跟住變蠢㗎<br />\n梗係返工keep住有競爭力 返工扮吓靚啦"},{"pid":"69b62688fc3e8bd93764a21562e4789efc53e28b","tid":972658,"uid":867,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T13:58:44.000Z","msg":"一個放工煮下飯一個放工返到嚟做下家務<br />\n兩個分擔下屋企不知幾寫意 利申未結婚唔知現實情況"},{"pid":"1548577a9e83d523db479b7cbf89fe365cdd0530","tid":972658,"uid":213270,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-07T14:05:34.000Z","msg":"最理想係賺錢買花戴，就算無左份工都唔會好拮据<br 